# Library
```{r}
library(synthpop)
library(labelled)
library(tidyverse)
set.seed(20122021)
```

# Loading Data
```{r}
load("cccu_complete1.RData")
```

# Simulate
```{r}
FAKE_cccu_complete1 = syn(data = cccu_complete1)
```


# Save sim data
```{r}
save(FAKE_cccu_complete1,
     file = "FAKE_cccu_complete1.RData")
```
